    -H "X-Admin-Token: qc-test-fred-2026" \
    -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
    -d '{"platform":"whatsapp","uid":"YOUR_NUMBER","free_checks_used":0}'

  Replace YOUR_NUMBER with your WhatsApp number in international format without + — e.g. 447863795638.



The free tier only gives 3/day — you can't set it to 999 directly. Easiest for testing is to give yourself a
  paid balance instead:

  curl -s -X POST https://web-production-1f0a4.up.railway.app/admin/set-balance \
    -H "X-Admin-Token: qc-test-fred-2026" \
    -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
    -d '{"platform":"whatsapp","uid":"YOUR_NUMBER","cents":24975}'

  That's 24,975 cents = 999 checks at 25¢ each. Fred will show your balance as paid and deduct normally from
  there.


